{"article_id":"AEQFkZSDrydyKlx3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"This latest report puts Romney on the defensive over his ties to Bain Capital .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Obama camp wages war","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"The Obama campaign went on the attack Thursday","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"after a bombshell report revealed","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that Mitt Romney was the CEO of Bain Capital for years longer","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"than he has previously admitted .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Obama deputy campaign manager Stephanie Cutter said","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"this new disclosure shows","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Romney is \" the most secretive candidate","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"to run for president","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"since Richard Nixon . \"","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"\" At every turn , at every piece of Mitt Romney ' s record or credential ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"whether it ' s Bain ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"whether it ' s his own personal finances ,","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"whether it ' s who is raising money for him or his time in the Statehouse in Massachusetts ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"there is an enormous cloud over Mitt Romney ' s record","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"because of his penchant for secrecy and not wanting to be transparent and open with the American people , \"","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Cutter said on a conference call with reporters .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"This latest report puts Romney on the defensive over his ties to Bain Capital , a central focus of the Obama campaign ' s attacks on the Republican ' s candidacy .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"It also plays into the Obama camp ' s charge","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that Romney is not being truthful and forthcoming about his finances and tax returns .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"The Romney campaign disputed the Boston Globe story","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"that found ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"based on documents","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"filed with the SEC ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that the former Massachusetts governor had served as the CEO at Bain until 2002 ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"although Romney has maintained","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"that he left active management of the firm in 1999 .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"\" The article is not accurate , \"","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Romney press secretary Andrea Saul said in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"\" As Bain Capital has said ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"as Governor Romney has said ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and as has been confirmed by independent fact checkers multiple times ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Governor Romney left Bain Capital in February of 1999","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to run the Olympics","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"and had no input on investments or management of companies after that point . \"","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"And Romney adviser Matt McDonald told","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"that \" Romney wasn ' t involved in any investment decisions .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"He was on the SEC filings","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"because he was still technically the owner","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"but hadn ' t transferred ownership to other partners . \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Cutter said","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"the Globe report should set off alarms for the American public","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"about trusting Romney ' s biography","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"- and","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that it also seriously undercuts any claims from his campaign","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that Romney is \" someone","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"who understands the real economy \" unlike President Barack Obama .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"\" When he left the Statehouse in Massachusetts ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"he and his senior staff took all the hard drives with them .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"And with those hard drives were really the record of the governorship of Mitt Romney .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"So that broke precedent in Massachusetts .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"And then finally , Mitt Romney ' s Olympic record [ is ] less than wholesome ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"shall we say ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"in terms of the decisions","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"that were made there ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"the contracts","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that were signed ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"and the basic operation of how Mitt Romney ran the Olympics , \"","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"The Globe story reports","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"that ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"according to Securities and Exchange Commission filings ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Romney did not leave Bain Capital in 1999","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"as he said","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"he had","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"but continued his tenure for three additional years .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"\" Government documents","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"filed by Mitt Romney and Bain Capital","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"say","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Romney remained chief executive and chairman of the firm three years beyond the date","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"he ceded control ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"even creating five new investment partnerships during that time , \"","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Globe reporters Callum Borchers and Christopher Rowland wrote .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":149,"left":76,"right":148,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":114,"right":147,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":94,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":91,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":79,"right